parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the tie rod can cause loss of vehicle control, especially during turns, which can lead to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle pulls to one side
the vehicle wanders or drifts during turns
the vehicle is difficult to steer
the vehicle goes out of control during turns
abnormal noises or vibrations are present during turns.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty seat belt buckle can lead to the seat belt being inoperable, increasing the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The plastic press release button breaks off
the seat belt buckle does not latch
the seat belt buckle is difficult to latch
the seat belt buckle is stuck
the seat belt is inoperable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning horn can lead to reduced safety on the road, as the driver may not be able to alert other drivers or pedestrians in emergency situations.
symptoms: The horn is inoperative
the horn is stuck and cannot be turned off
the horn emits a continuous or intermittent sound without being pressed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: An electrical system failure in the horn circuit can cause the horn to malfunction, leading to reduced safety on the road.
symptoms: The horn is inoperative
the horn is stuck and cannot be turned off
the horn emits a continuous or intermittent sound without being pressed
the horn connector needs to be disconnected to stop the horn from operating.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Tire Failure Due to Ply Separation
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Tire failure due to ply separation can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially result in serious injuries or fatalities, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Tire blowouts
tire vibration
tire damage indicating imminent ply separation
sudden loss of air pressure
unusual tire noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Defective tires can lead to sudden and unexpected tire failures, which can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Tire blowouts
tire vibration
tire damage
sudden loss of air pressure
unusual tire noise
tire failure without warning.
